Administrative plugin, used to debug auth problems and settings.
This plugin is only for testing purposes.
If DEBUG has no _DEBUG_LOGIN bit set, only the admin user can call it,
which is of no real use.

Warning! This may display DB and user passwords in cleartext. We think we
cleared everything out though.

!!! Usage
<verbatim>
  <?plugin _AuthInfo userid||=AdminUser ?>
</verbatim>

!!! Arguments

userid:
  default: current user

!!! Example

See DebugAuthInfo

!!! Authors
[Jeff Dairiki|PhpWiki:JeffDairiki], [Reini Urban|PhpWiki:ReiniUrban]

!!! See Also

DebugAuthInfo is the corresponding Help:ActionPage.

